he VM is powered on.\n\nor\n\nFrom a PowerCLI command prompt while connected to the ESXi host or vCenter server run the following command:\n\nGet-VM "VM Name" | Get-AdvancedSetting -Name isolation.tools.memSchedFakeSampleStats.disable\n\nIf the virtual machine advanced setting isolation.tools.memSchedFakeSampleStats.disable does not exist or is not set to true, this is a finding.','Imported data from UCF - DISA') from dual;
